Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.55,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.47,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That event is burned into my eyes and won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:56.72,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnCambria\pos(358,128)\fs32\3c&H34444B&\c&HA8CAD5&}Morita Technology Research Office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.11,clover,,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:56.72,clover,,0,0,0,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:01:59.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's up, Tatsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:03.06,clover,,0,0,0,,President, it's about the final interview for our new hires...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:06.75,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hire a guy who can make good curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.70,clover,,0,0,0,,President, can't you be a little more serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.71,clover,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Check it out, Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.53,clover,,0,0,0,,The Remote Control Walker is finally complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:25.21,clover,,0,0,0,,First, you set your easily lost household AC, TV, and VCR remotes on the Remote Control Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Then, you call for it after leaving it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Mr. Remote Control?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:37.93,clover,,0,0,0,,And, like magic, they gather towards the voice no matter where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.20,clover,,0,0,0,,What do ya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:43.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, President... No, Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.62,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:49.00,clover,,0,0,0,,I think they're unnecessary if you keep the room clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.83,clover,,0,0,0,,What the heck, Tatsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.32,clover,,0,0,0,,You've always been like that! Always making sound arguments!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.36,clover,,0,0,0,,You're a boring man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:03:01.75,clover,,0,0,0,,"You shouldn't skip out on cleaning" and "You can't draw eyebrows on a dog face with a marker."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Those aren't called arguments. They're basic rules of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:09.07,clover,,0,0,0,,To begin with, you're screwed up, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Whenever we slice up a watermelon, you just go and bite the top off every piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:16.39,clover,,0,0,0,,What should we do? All the candidates are already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.69,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, come on. You're still bitter about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.64,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You sure are persistent. That happened back in kindergarten!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:21.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Let them hear it! They'll quickly realize the true form of the Morita Tech Research Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:21.39,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No! It was in fifth grade! The little league camp! In the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.36,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll be starting the final interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Those of you whose number is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Forget it. That's so tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.14,clover,,0,0,0,,Instead of hearing you talk, let's see your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:37.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Please make an airplane using the materials in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.60,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll hire the guy who gets it to fly the farthest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.50,clover,,0,0,0,,The time limit is three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.34,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm also forcing all of you to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.71,clover,,0,0,0,,P-President...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:47.88,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll make one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.36,clover,,0,0,0,,All right, my sons will enter the battle as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:56.63,clover,,0,0,0,,If you lose to an elementary schooler, not only will you not get hired, you'll be doing ten laps!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Pushy as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:09.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,This odd company that my father founded was small but lively...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:14.43,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and the mechanical parts that my father designed were popular even overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.87,thoughts,,0,0,0,,What happened back then is burned into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.30,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The airplane that flew gracefully through the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:30.80,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good job, Shinobu! As expected of my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.81,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and my father's eyes that proudly gazed upon my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:37.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And the sight of my father's young admirers who were giving it their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.10,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.26,clover,,0,0,0,,So, Shinobu wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.78,clover,,0,0,0,,No one's being hired this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.40,clover,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.95,clover,,0,0,0,,P-Please give me another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I definitely want to work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:59.20,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I admire President Morita so much that this is my third try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:05:01.51,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And the profile of that person standing next to me, holding a plane that, like mine, wouldn't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:08.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad! I found Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.34,clover,,0,0,0,,He fell into a hole inside the cement factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.15,clover,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.66,clover,,0,0,0,,But there were a bunch of Japanese plums...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Never mind the plums!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad, we need to get him to the doctor soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.93,clover,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight! We're gonna go fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:29.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru, please go back to the Company and tell everyone that we found Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.02,clover,,0,0,0,,O-Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.06,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.33,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Just earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.79,clover,,0,0,0,,I was in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.46,clover,,0,0,0,,When I was running to get Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:53.63,clover,,0,0,0,,I fell on the stone steps at the shrine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.67,clover,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-kun, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:04.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:15.19,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Uncle Negishi was my Dad's childhood friend, best friend, and an important business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.72,clover,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:25.42,clover,,0,0,0,,So Shinobu got enticed by the Japanese plums and fell into a hole at that abandoned factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.25,clover,,0,0,0,,That can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:32.29,clover,,0,0,0,,He's just like your father when he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:35.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Wild and greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.05,clover,,0,0,0,,If a kid in a classroom to the east were sick and absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:41.40,clover,,0,0,0,,...he'd fly over and eat that kid's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.08,clover,,0,0,0,,If there were a fight to the north...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:46.18,clover,,0,0,0,,...he'd also fly over and make an even bigger mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:50.31,clover,,0,0,0,,He really did whatever he felt like, damn him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.45,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Even so, he was loved by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:01.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Number Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:02.64,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The pitcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.20,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...general manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.08,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...and owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.60,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...Morita Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:13.11,clover,,0,0,0,,He was never afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.28,clover,,0,0,0,,When he should've have been really scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.92,clover,,0,0,0,,...maybe he was holding it back with a strong will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:22.22,clover,,0,0,0,,...or perhaps the sense of fear was missing from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:26.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm so close to him, I still can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:30.88,clover,,0,0,0,,He'd be smiling, even if he's the final batter in a losing game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.61,clover,,0,0,0,,A pinch only seemed like a chance to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.04,clover,,0,0,0,,He had so much that I didn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.34,clover,,0,0,0,,I was envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.56,clover,,0,0,0,,He was so loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.82,clover,,0,0,0,,So bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.29,clover,,0,0,0,,I was blinded and choked on my own breath so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.83,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:00.77,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Even for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:06.27,clover,,0,0,0,,I always thought that there must be something that only I am capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.39,clover,,0,0,0,,I wanted to think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:17.79,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:19.86,clover,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.99,sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs36\fnFutura LT ExtraBold\pos(358,412)\frx25}STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.51,clover,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.83,clover,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.49,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Back then, I hadn't noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:37.23,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...but he was already afflicted with a terminal illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.13,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I can understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Here's your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.81,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm not Dad. It's Tatsuo, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:55.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:01.02,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right, he's all grown up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.70,clover,,0,0,0,,You know Ricchan from the tobacco shop? The girl Tatsuo liked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:09.20,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she won't come marry into our family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Ricchan is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Negishi-san, please be admitted to the hospital right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.91,clover,,0,0,0,,But once I go in, I can't leave, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to work until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.89,clover,,0,0,0,,There's a reason for me to keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:38.20,clover,,0,0,0,,If I die, who will take care of Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.94,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd always wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:50.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Why this world is split between those who are gifted and those who aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:55.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Why there are those who are loved and those who aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.62,sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs36\fnFutura LT ExtraBold\pos(358,420)\frx20}STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Who made the split?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Where was the split in the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:07.75,clover,,0,0,0,,No... Was there even a split in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:15.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was already decided the moment we were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.65,clover,,0,0,0,,If that were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.65,clover,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.51,clover,,0,0,0,,What was my life for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, now about the next topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.93,clover,,0,0,0,,It's about the patent rights for that motor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:59.43,clover,,0,0,0,,I believe it would be better if we placed the company's name instead of the president's name on the patent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:09.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Also, we should gather more funds to expand the factory, so I'd like to issue more stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.01,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Please do as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm bad with that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.49,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Tatsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, please show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.74,clover,,0,0,0,,...that you are human like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:41.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Or, if not, please make me understand that you're from a different world than mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:45.91,clover,,0,0,0,,...crush me to bits, and return me to the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.86,clover,,0,0,0,,The rights to the patent have been completely written over to the company...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.30,clover,,0,0,0,,...and the preparations for increasing the stocks is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.33,clover,,0,0,0,,We just have to decide what day to make the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:00.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Well done, Mr. Negishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:05.79,clover,,0,0,0,,It must have been difficult to betray your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:12.67,clover,,0,0,0,,In return, I'll promise that you'll see compensation befitting your courage and anguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Please show me, Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.43,clover,,0,0,0,,...whether your light is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:28.54,clover,,0,0,0,,Whether nothing could make it fade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.53,clover,,0,0,0,,What a dirty laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Call in a reform company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:52.59,clover,,0,0,0,,We should switch to a layout that will yield better productivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:58.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Dear me, dear me, Mr. Morita. I'm pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:05.50,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd like to welcome you today as our most important technician in Floyd Electric Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:09.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Although your business will now belong to Floyd Electric Corporation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.16,clover,,0,0,0,,...I will promise funding and salary to allow you and your employees to maintain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:18.41,clover,,0,0,0,,...no, surpass the work that you have been doing up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tatsuo. What's this guy talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:30.05,clover,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't even ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.29,clover,,0,0,0,,The talk is probably a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.29,clover,,0,0,0,,The conditions are rather favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change about the workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:43.42,clover,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to freely work on your research under a bigger source of funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.94,clover,,0,0,0,,See? It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:52.34,clover,,0,0,0,,You really got me, Tatsuo. I've lost this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.24,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:14:01.96,clover,,0,0,0,,I love money, but I hate being made to work with someone else's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Please think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Everyone's pay will double...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.54,clover,,0,0,0,,...and you'll be getting a top-class salary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:16.26,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to punch your lights out, but I'll refrain for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Take care of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:21.25,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't want to ask you, but this alone I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.01,clover,,0,0,0,,If you betray my request, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Got it, Tatsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.82,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:46.29,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can finally go to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I hadn't been able to sleep lately for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:56.67,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But now I feel like I can finally sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:02.24,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Deeply... like sinking into mud...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tatsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't do it if you're gonna apologize later, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.40,clover,,0,0,0,,You were tricked, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:25.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:30.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Again, this contract states that we'll be paying you as our employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:37.04,clover,,0,0,0,,In the event that you pass away, unfortunately, all rights will be transferred to Floyd Electric Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.54,clover,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't just agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.56,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:46.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll hate you until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.07,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll hate you even if you're reborn a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:57.13,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kotoba ga ima tsumatte shimattara\NIf I can't bring myself to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:54.69,clover,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.52,clover,,0,0,0,,You two shouldn't hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:03.78,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}bokura no natsu wa koko de owateshimaisou\N...our summer together might end right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.58,clover,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.41,clover,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.76,clover,,0,0,0,,I can't! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:03.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Why, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:10.62,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}jyouzu ni waraeteru jishin nanka\NI laughed, even though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:17.12,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aru wake nai no ni demo waratta\N...I had no confidence that I could laugh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:21.50,clover,,0,0,0,,It's my job to curse and hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:24.04,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fumitsubushita kakato wo hakinaoshitara\NOnce you put your flattened heels back on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.09,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.26,clover,,0,0,0,,So you two should move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:31.77,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tame iki wo gutto nomikonde arukidasou\N...let's swallow our sighs and start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.24,clover,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:42.67,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}yuugure wo nukete iku kaze wa aki no nioi wo fukunderu\NThe evening breeze brings in autumn's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:43.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:56.02,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}zutto kyou to onaji hibi ga negawanakutemo tsudzuku to omotteta\NI was thinking things would stay the same without having to wish for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.04,clover,,0,0,0,,I have some regrets, but why don't we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:48.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:13.73,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}akkepanashi no mado no mukougawa de\NBeyond the open window...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:23.90,sign,,0,0,0,,100 hours playback!! Utilizing the best power motor in this galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad made this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Floyd Electric...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:35.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Dad's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.34,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:44.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's run, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:45.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:17:59.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.19,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.65,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Got it? Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.87,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Don't let the dark emotions catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.87,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Run towards the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.64,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I can't, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.48,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I can't run fast like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.88,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.38,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I understand how Uncle felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:45.94,sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs36\fnFutura LT ExtraBold\pos(358,412)\frx25}STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.92,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\fs50\bord0\b1\pos(358,260)\c&HF8FEFE&}Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.54,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,260)\fs50\fnSegoe Print\b1\bord0\c&HF8FEFE&}I was always envious of my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.72,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,260)\fs50\fnSegoe Print\b1\bord0\c&HF8FEFE&}And
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:12.09,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,260)\fs50\fnSegoe Print\b1\bord0\c&HF8FEFE&}I was envious of you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:16.10,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean, Dad, I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.28,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:24.37,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to think that there's something that only I could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.73,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.15,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.12,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.95,thoughts,,0,0,0,,No! Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.41,thoughts,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Get in the bed if you're gonna sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.51,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything else for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:58.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.01,clover,,0,0,0,,You can go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.38,clover,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:06.86,clover,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll stay here, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:16.53,clover,,0,0,0,,The car is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:17.82,clover,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.25,clover,,0,0,0,,We'll send them all to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:27.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.16,clover,,0,0,0,,The wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:41.09,clover,,0,0,0,,It's so windy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the displays outside will be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.35,clover,,0,0,0,,It's finally the Hamabi Festival, and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.90,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.16,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even notice it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:05.03,thoughts,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could've predicted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.82,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The event that would soon happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And the lives that we'll lead from here on out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:15.70,thoughts,,0,0,0,,None of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:29.88,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:29.88,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:40.34,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:40.34,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.76,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.76,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:52.89,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:52.89,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:22:06.37,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:22:06.37,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:09.11,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:09.11,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.97,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.97,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:16.31,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:16.31,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:25.01,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:25.01,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.41,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.41,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
